{"title":"2020-05-22","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<p>寛容の精神でーなどと言いつつ、このご時勢で気にせずソーシャルディスタンスを詰めてくるおっさん、うっかり蹴り○したくなるわ。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>金沢でも UberEats の配達を発見した。数ヶ月前はまだ未進出だったはずなのに、さすが海外企業、動きがはやいわ。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>色違いゲット。赤かっこいい。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-05-22/20200522-194028-Screenshot_20200522-194028.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-05-22/20200522-194028-Screenshot_20200522-194028.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-05-22/20200522-194140-Screenshot_20200522-194140.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-05-22/20200522-194140-Screenshot_20200522-194140.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記","updated":"2020-05-24T07:22:18","published":"2020-05-24T07:22:18"}